    new subsection covers: singlefile/lazy-import incompatibility; Option 2 (separate web resources)
    pattern as a reference; link to R3 bundle-size investigation memo; explicit note that implementation
    is deferred per OC-R4-04.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per spec DR-05 + plan §4 Phase 1 D-2 + OC-R4-04: R3 surfaced a heavy-library bundle-size problem
