      split heavy libs into separate Code Page web resources loaded lazily. R3 documented but did not
      implement. R4 scope cap (OC-R4-04): ADR amendment only — implementation deferred indefinitely. This
      task captures the pattern so future authors know the option exists and what blocks it (singlefile
      build constraint).
    </background>
